@startuml
!pragma teoz true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
title 图26  统计报表生成顺序图

actor "票务管理员" as Admin
participant "Vue 看板页" as FE
participant "StatisticsController" as Ctrl
participant "StatisticsService" as SS
database "MySQL\n(ticket_order / ticket_item / show_schedule)" as DB
participant "ECharts" as Chart

Admin -> FE : 打开数据看板
FE -> Ctrl : GET /api/stat/dashboard
Ctrl -> SS : getDashboard(dateRange)
SS -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*), SUM(amount)\nFROM ticket_order WHERE date=today
DB --> SS : 今日订单数 / 销售额
SS -> DB : 近7天订单按日聚合
DB --> SS : 趋势数据
SS -> DB : 热门演出 TOP10
DB --> SS : 排行榜
SS -> DB : 各场次上座率\n(已售/总座位)
DB --> SS : 上座率数据
SS -> DB : 订单状态分布
DB --> SS : 状态聚合
SS --> Ctrl : DashboardVO
Ctrl --> FE : 200 OK + 数据
FE -> Chart : 渲染折线 / 柱状 / 饼图
Chart --> Admin : 显示数据看板
@enduml
